{"tid":896423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不忿送巴士車尾襲車長　躁婦拒捕被扯爛衫","createTime":"2018-11-10T04:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T06:23:24.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"385098a0e9cf3b83deb61e44540d60067a6f56b4","tid":896423,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:19:16.000Z","msg":"今（9日）早上11時35分，一名61歲姓陳婦人，在東涌逸東邨巴士總站，擬搭乘開往荃灣方向的E31路線龍運巴士。據現場消息稱，疑因她趕至站內時，已見巴士駛出「送車尾」，於是上前攔阻以身擋車。其間有現場職員見狀，上前勸阻，惟有人卻出手掌摑56歲車長，車長受傷倒地。有人疑見闖禍一度欲離場，卻遭23歲站長截停。糾纏間，站長報稱右手腕受傷，而婦人的格仔上衣衫袖亦遭扯爛。<br />\n警員其後接報到場，經初步調查，以涉普通襲擊將婦人拘捕。事件中，兩名受傷車長及站長需送往北大嶼山醫院檢驗。<br />\n龍運巴士公司發言人指，對於有車長和前線同事遇襲，龍運十分憤慨及強烈譴責襲擊的行為，龍運會配合警方的調查，公司法律部會全力協助受襲同事。龍運強調，襲擊車長屬刑事罪行，一經定罪可判罰款及監禁，龍運呼籲乘客切勿以身試法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2072795/org/08e8f1bfdfce317ab7277a1e928e4ab7.jpg/kOykwvP_sho58rUvPh_Eu9e-LYnFe3G59KdRD_SnUQ8?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2072795%2Forg%2F08e8f1bfdfce317ab7277a1e928e4ab7.jpg%2FkOykwvP_sho58rUvPh_Eu9e-LYnFe3G59KdRD_SnUQ8%3Fv%3Dw480&h=ee03a9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2072796/org/fdd17053b8dba50db1d3ddf8d9f23d58.jpg/Fc2DIK36O274j32QTu_REUOhVpjovfxCN05rQTdOa0E?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2072796%2Forg%2Ffdd17053b8dba50db1d3ddf8d9f23d58.jpg%2FFc2DIK36O274j32QTu_REUOhVpjovfxCN05rQTdOa0E%3Fv%3Dw480&h=50575594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2072885/org/4a39696030602540ba85c49ccb234cca.jpg/kllLQ65EkPe8eE50ntI8FUG9fKj_2MXow3P9mMNz_Zg?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2072885%2Forg%2F4a39696030602540ba85c49ccb234cca.jpg%2FkllLQ65EkPe8eE50ntI8FUG9fKj_2MXow3P9mMNz_Zg%3Fv%3Dw480&h=4a4ca663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2073398/org/3ea616528aedcc91b03a7f05a5